Frankie is the owner of Frankie's Fishing Emporium in Port Piscarilius. He is wearing parts of the angler's outfit and is toting a fishing rod. He buys and sells raw fish, including raw sharks, but has no stock.

Players can help him collect fresh fish and deposit them into the cooling chest inside his store for Piscarilius favour.

Due to his fishing rod, Frankie's detection area is about twice as large as other NPCs.
